## Configuration Backup

### ğŸ’¾ Backup Tasks
- [ ] **Backup Proxmox configuration**:
  ```bash
  # Create backup of key configurations
  tar czf /root/proxmox-config-backup-$(date +%Y%m%d).tar.gz \
      /etc/pve/ \
      /etc/network/interfaces \
      /etc/hosts \
      /etc/resolv.conf \
      /root/.ssh/
  ```
- [ ] **Document customizations** made
- [ ] **Save script logs**: `/var/log/proxmox-post-install.log`

### ğŸ“ Documentation
- [ ] **Document installed packages** with versions
- [ ] **Record configuration changes** made
- [ ] **Note any custom repository additions**
- [ ] **Document SSH keys added**

